## SECTION 5 — AWF WORKFLOW PROTOCOL

When user triggers a workflow (e.g., /plan, /code, /debug):
1. Read the matching file in `ROOT D\<workflow>.md`
2. Follow the phases step-by-step
3. Report progress at each phase

